(1)
604 Flatbush Ave., west side, between Parkside Ave., and Westbury Court, showing The "Colony Inn", built by the Grandfather of Judge GG...etn Martense. This building was occupied by John Franklin in 1842, and subsequently sold by his heirs, to Dr. Norfolk in 1873. About 1923 it
was demolished to make room for modern apartments.
1922.

1922.
